						<div class="postbody">I still haven't written a full scrolling engine, myself.  I had most of the metatile decoding and static screen loading code written, but I was just making the level data manually in the source code.
<br />
<br />That opentume program looks like a nice level editor, it was used with several commercial games.  It needs custom programs written to convert the data to a format for your program though.  (and apparantly the author of the program doesn't have access to the NES-related source code to it anymore)</div>

